item.title: Crawling
item.description: This Discord bot can crawl all Elon Musk’s activities on Twitter. It will check if there are any tweets, retweets, or replies by Elon Musk every 60 seconds. Start the crawling process: ?crawling Stop the crawling process: ?stop_crawling

item.title: Image editing
item.description: We can change your face to Elon Ma. Everyone can be Elon Ma! Attach an image and enter the following command: ?image
